]], [[List of Power Rangers Super Megaforce episodes|List of ''Super Megaforce'' episodes]])\n| preceded_by              = ''[[Power Rangers Samurai|Power Rangers Super Samurai]]''\n| followed_by              = ''[[Power Rangers Dino Charge]]''\n}}\n\n'''''Power Rangers Megaforce''''' is the twentieth season of the long-running [[United States|American]] [[children's television program]] ''[[Power Rangers]]''. The show is produced by [[Saban Capital Group|SCG Power Rangers]] and began airing on [[Nickelodeon]] on February 2, 2013.<ref name=\"TV Guide\">{{cite news | url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/Power-Rangers-Megaforce-Premiere-1059159.aspx?rss=news&partnerid=spi&profileid=05 | title=Exclusive: Find Out When Power Rangers Megaforce Premieres and Get a First Look at the Cast | work=TV Guide | date=January 16, 2013 | accessdate=January 16, 2013 | author=Ross, Robyn}}</ref> The show was part of the ''Power Rangers'' 20th anniversary.<ref name=MarVista>{{cite news|last=Dickson|first=Jeremy|title=MarVista unveils new Power Rangers Megaforce series|url=http://kidscreen.com/2012/08/29/marvista-unveils-new-power-rangers-megaforce-series/|accessdate=September 8, 2012|newspaper=KidScreen|date=August 30, 2012}}</ref><ref name=MarVista2>{{cite news|last=Whittock|first=Jesse|title=MarVista powers up for Mip|url=http://www.c21media.net/archives/87172|accessdate=September 8, 2012|newspaper=C21Media|date=August 29, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Saban Celebrates Power Rangers, Paul Frank|url=http://digital.licensemag.com/nxtbooks/advanstar/license_daily_20120612/index.php?startid=12|accessdate=September 8, 2012|newspaper=License Show Daily|date=June 12, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Saban Creates Power Rangers Avatars|url=http://www.licensemag.com/licensemag/Entertainment/Saban-Creates-Power-Rangers-Avatars/ArticleStandard/Article/detail/782010|accessdate=September 8, 2012|newspaper=LicenseMag|date=July 19, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Cynopsis: Kids! 06/12/12|url=